Gaussian

K <- 5
## data
s <- NormalSampler(n = 100,
                   L = 1000,
                   K = K,
                   prop.outlier = 0.2,
                   sigma = 0.2,
                   c = 0.6,
                   mean.B = 0.0,
                   sd.B = 1.0,
                   sd.mu = 1.0,
                   mean.mu = 0.5)
RidgeVsLasso(s,
             method.K = K, exp.rep = 1)
Hypothesis testing comparison
